<p id="fs-idm32532304">(b) preparation of a soluble silver salt for silver plating<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
<math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>Ag</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>HNO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>Ag</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>HNO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idm68463232">(c) preparation of strontium hydroxide by electrolysis of a solution of strontium chloride<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
